xnoise (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=low
  * add support for dockable media sources (Categories: Playlists, Media Collection, Stores)
  * add onboard dbus service (not bound to mpris)
  * add new azlyrics plugin
  * add automatic thumbnail generation for videos
  * refresh xnoise layout
  * merge cyclic-save-state plugin int xnoise
  * newly done application button for compact layout
  * add possibility to name streams on import
  * add keybinding for increasing/decreasing playback volume
  * speed up tracklist rendering
  * add handler for moving tracks to trash
  * add handler for showing media in file manager
  * add suport for tag embedded images
  * update some translation
  * fixes for utf8 handling
  * fix playlist stream import
  * lastfm: fix for multiple scrobble on fast track changes
  * fix automatic linebreaks for dockable media and media browser
  * optimizations
  * many more fixes

 -- Jörn Magens <shuerhaaken@googlemail.com>  Tue, 03 Apr 2012 12:28:38 +0200



xnoise (0.1.31) unstable; urgency=low
  * port xnoise to gtk+-3.0
  * add option for disabling video subtitles
  * stop using uris for the title search
  * mediabrowser: gtk3 compatible font rendering with linebreaks
  * update some translation
  * lastfm plugin: make scrobbling optional (cover fetching can be used without logging an user into lastfm)
  * remove deprecated HBox/VBox widgets
  * use icons for drag'n'drop
  * drop dependency to libunique (now gio's application class)
  * introduce gtk2 branch in version control
  * remove old versions of notification and soundmenu plugin
  * many bug fixes

 -- Jörn Magens <shuerhaaken@googlemail.com>  Fri, 20 Jan 2012 17:38:52 +0100


